_sText:
This map was originally made for Garry's Mod deathrun for a mapping contest. It ended up getting first place. I decided to make a version for css. It is very well balanced for lots or little people.

It should be able to handle more than 64 players.

There was originally a working secret in the Garry's Mod version, but it doesn't work in CSS and I didn't feel like fixing it.
